title: Kenny Chesney Stops By For The Friday Morning Conversation + Lunchbox Shares A Baby Box Health Update
itunes:title: Kenny Chesney Stops By For The Friday Morning Conversation + Lunchbox Shares A Baby Box Health Update
description:
Kenny Chesney stops by to celebrate the release of his album "Songs For The Saints." Lunchbox shares an exciting update about his newborn son's health. Also, Morgan #2 shares a listener's 'Tell Me Something Good' story about the show getting her out of a traffic stop ticket.
